PersistentDialogue.Script:
GetCardDataByIndex
		Log/Fetching card information from AllCards list at index -VAL:Index-.
		SetString/CardName,LIST{AllCards,-VAL:Index-}
		SetVal/Rarity,=:LIST{AllCardsToRarity,-VAL:Index-}
		SetString/RarityName,LIST{RarityToName,-VAL:Rarity-}
		SetVal/RarityCost,=:LIST{RarityToCost,-VAL:Rarity-}
